Monica Seles File:Monica Seles.jpeg Country Yugoslavia Biographical Information Birthplace Novi Sad, SR Serbia, SFR Yugoslavia Physical Information Tennis Information Plays Left-handed (two-handed both sides) Singles Grand Slam results Doubles Grand Slam Doubles results Last updated on date of today.

Monica Seles (born December 2, 1973) is a former Yugoslav world no. 1 professional tennis player and a member of the International Tennis Hall of Fame.
